### Test Jira API Endpoints

### 1. Login first to get token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. Create Project (use token from login)
POST http://localhost:3000/jira/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Test Project",
  "key": "TEST",
  "description": "This is a test project"
}

### 3. Get all projects
GET http://localhost:3000/jira/projects
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get specific project
GET http://localhost:3000/jira/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Create Task
POST http://localhost:3000/jira/projects/PROJECT_ID_HERE/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Test Task",
  "description": "<p>This is a test task</p>",
  "columnId": "COLUMN_ID_HERE",
  "type": "TASK",
  "priority": "MEDIUM"
}

### 6. Get Task
GET http://localhost:3000/jira/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Update Task
PUT http://localhost:3000/jira/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### 8. Move Task
PUT http://localhost:3000/jira/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/move
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "columnId": "NEW_COLUMN_ID_HERE",
  "position": 1000
}

### 9. Add Comment
POST http://localhost:3000/jira/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "content": "This is a test comment"
}

### 10. Delete Task
DELETE http://localhost:3000/jira/tasks/TASK_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
